https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F161796243843515_865358758951492&title=%09Implications%20and%20responsibilities%3A%20AI%20in%20teaching%20and%20learning%20in%20the%20Commonwealth.Artificial%20intelligence%20%28AI%29%20has%20significant%20implications%20for%20teaching%20and%20learning.%20This%20also%20brings%20into%20play%20the%20huge%20responsibilities%20related%20to%20ethics%2C%20privacy%20and%20data%20security%20for%20post-secondary%20educational%20institutions.%20A%20recent%20report%20released%20by%20%23COL4D%20indicates%20that%20about%2065%25%20of%20%23Commonwealth%20institutions%20do%20not%20have%20any%20policy%20or%20strategy%20related%20to%20integrating%20%23AI%20in%20teaching%20and%20learning.The%20report%20is%20based%20on%20a%20survey%20of%20post-secondary%20institutions%20in%20the%20Commonwealth%2C%20including%20COL%E2%80%99s%20partner%20institutions.%20It%20presents%20findings%20from%20the%20stakeholder%20surveys%20to%20highlight%20the%20existence%20of%20AI%20policies%2C%20areas%20of%20application%20of%20AI%2C%20the%20main%20challenges%20and%20benefits%20of%20AI%2C%20and%20expectations%20about%20the%20future%20of%20AI.Post-secondary%20institutions%20are%20largely%20focusing%20on%20the%20use%20of%20AI%20in%20teaching%20and%20learning%20to%20empower%20teachers%2C%20followed%20by%20supporting%20the%20improvement%20of%20learner%20outcomes.%20Current%20use%20of%20AI%20tools%20is%20limited%20to%20only%20editing%20of%20documents.%20Those%20who%20are%20not%20using%20AI%20tools%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20training%20and%20knowledge%20about%20AI%20among%20faculty%20members.%20Interestingly%2C%20lack%20of%20training%20on%20AI%20is%20a%20common%20issue%20amongst%20all%20the%20institutions%20surveyed.%20While%20the%20institutions%20are%20optimistic%20about%20integrating%20AI%20into%20teaching%20and%20learning%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20policy%20is%20a%20major%20concern%20for%20implementation.Professor%20Peter%20Scott%20%40peter_scott%2C%20President%20and%20CEO%20of%20COL%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20report%20is%20a%20step%20towards%20systematically%20addressing%20the%20issue%20of%20integrating%20AI%20into%20teaching%20and%20learning%20in%20the%20educational%20institutions%20of%20the%20Commonwealth.%20I%20urge%20leaders%20in%20these%20institutions%20to%20treat%20this%20issue%20as%20a%20priority%20and%20to%20develop%20policies%20and%20guidelines%20for%20students%20and%20teachers%20to%20help%20them%20use%20the%20available%20AI%20tools%20appropriately%20and%20with%20caution%20to%20enhance%20the%20quality%20of%20learning%20and%20teaching%20overall.%E2%80%9DCOL%20is%20committed%20to%20promoting%20the%20appropriate%20and%20effective%20use%20of%20technologies%20to%20improve%20access%20to%20quality%20education%20and%20training.%20AI%20training%20has%20already%20made%20inroads%20into%20the%20capacity%20building%20for%20course%20development%20and%20open%20educational%20resources.Full%20report%20available%20here%3A%20hdl.handle.net%2F11599%2F5605%23ArtificialIntelligence%20%23AIForLearning%20%23AIInTeaching%20%23StudentDiversity%20%23AcademicSuccess%20%09%09,
